title.rendered: BOUNCE BACK AFTER WINTER BREAK |+ TRAVEL MEALS & WORKOUTS

content.rendered:
HAPPY NEW YEARRRRR!!! Woooohhooo let’s make 2017 YOUR YEAR!
This video actually contains a LOT! I show you a little of what I was up to on my trip to Anguilla, a travel/on the road workout, what I ate on vacay, AND ended it by giving you tips on how to bounce back after winter break or vacation. Watch the whole thing to see it all!!
Love,
Katie
